data.text:
More

Haus Zeder is located at 1030 metre above sea level in the Southern part of the Black forest. The Cedar House in the Black Forest can be used as seminar group house of associations, clubs, hikers, bikers, companies, private families. We hope that you will feel comfortable at Haus Zeder - whether you have come for the peace and quiet or whether you are making use of the variety of activities available in the area.
